These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, car, taxi, van
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, egyptian, thai, japanese
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, blood-red, brown, apricot
 1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
 2. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
 3. the person who likes brown is not to the right of the person who likes blood-red##8
 4. the person who likes blood-red is not to the left of the japanese##8
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is in an even position##4
 6. the person driving the car is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
 7. the colombian is the person who likes emerald##1
 8. the person who likes brown is not the japanese##6
 9. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
10. the person driving the taxi is not to the right of the thai##8
11. the person driving the car is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
12. the person who likes blood-red is between the person driving the taxi and the egyptian##2
13. the person who likes brown and the thai have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |     3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | taxi | car      | van | jet-ski |
| Job           | thai | japanese | egyptian      | colombian |
| Music-Genre   | brown        | blood-red            | apricot    | emerald |

