.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, train, airplane, car
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, collecting, hiking, card-games
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, amaryllis, aconite, lily
 1. the person who's hobby is hiking is not to the right of the person who growstulip##8
 2. the person driving the train is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8
 3. the person who growsamaryllis and the person who's hobby is video-games have the same parity positions##9
 4. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
 5. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 6. the person driving the ship is not to the left of the person driving the train##8
 7. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the right of the person driving the car##8
 8. the person who growsamaryllis is between the person driving the train and the person driving the airplane##2
 9. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
10. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
11. the person who's hobby is video-games is not to the left of the person who growslily##8
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the right of the person who growstulip##8
13. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
14. the person who's hobby is hiking is not to the left of the person driving the car##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage      | train | ship   | airplane     | car     |
| Music-Genre   | collecting    | video-games   | card-games      | hiking    |
| Sport         | lily   | amaryllis | aconite | tulip |

