.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, electrician, engineer, fisherman
City: rome, nizza, new-york, berlin
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, game, montecristo, bongani
 1. the nurse is not to the left of the person traveling to rome##8
 2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the electrician##1
 3. the person traveling to new-york is the nurse##1
 4. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere between the person traveling to berlin and the game-smoker##7
 5. the fisherman and the person traveling to rome have different parity positions##9
 6. the montecristo-smoker is not to the right of the nurse##8
 7. the montecristo-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to berlin##5
 8. the game-smoker is somewhere to the right of the fisherman##5
 9. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
10. the oliveros-smoker is between the person traveling to rome and the bongani-smoker##2
11. the electrician is not the person traveling to rome##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | fisherman | engineer     | nurse  | electrician |
| Nationality   | nizza       | rome    | new-york | berlin |
| Pet           | montecristo       | game | oliveros     | bongani  |

