 8. the prince-smoker is the chinese##1
 9. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the left of the bolivar-smoker##5
10. the prince-smoker is between the french and the dannemann-smoker##2
11. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the brazilian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | berlin  | colone        | nizza  | london |
| Hobby      | tiparillo  | prince    | dannemann | bolivar |
