 8. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
 9. the person traveling to boston is not to the right of the person traveling to london##8
10. the person playing monopoly is in an even position##4
11. the person traveling to boston is not to the right of the person traveling to london##8
