.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-20::.
4 different games are played: poker, billiard, domino, backgammon
House: colonial, victorian, ranch-style, wooden
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, dannemann, bolivar, bluemaster
 1. the colonial house is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
 2. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
 3. the dannemann-smoker is not the colonial house##6
 4. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 5. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the left of the dannemann-smoker##5
 6. the person playing poker is somewhere to the left of the person playing domino##5
 7. the person playing domino and the dannemann-smoker have different parity positions##9
 8. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
 9. the victorian house is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
10. the person playing poker is not to the right of the person playing billiard##8
11. the colonial house is not the dannemann-smoker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |       4       |
| Nationality   | poker | billiard    | domino   | backgammon       |
| Pet           | victorian    | ranch-style   | colonial | wooden        |
| Sport         | bluemaster  | fonseca | bolivar     | dannemann |

 